{"tid":788594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友唔鍾意用套 今日終於出事….","createTime":"2018-08-21T14:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T15:26:17.000Z","uid":123991,"like":5,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd2cdf06d079e02c8be598bff1457aa0383dc58","tid":788594,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n話說女朋友成日唔鐘意用套 <br />\n覺得用咗套個感覺唔同 好唔舒服<br />\n我少少串佢話我夠知啦 但係用咗安全啲呀嘛<br />\n我成日都勸佢唔好貪一時嘅感覺陣間後悔<br />\n但係佢都唔聽我講<br />\n點知頭先佢同我講佢去咗藥房行一轉話就出咗事<br />\n原來啱先畀人撞一撞就跌咗個電話落地 隻角咁就崩咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知畀咩反應佢好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8683f0b1941747a33fd27796be6c0a5b945750","tid":788594,"uid":14536,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"b1d4b7acaab9fbf6e72b0bfe80624d2cddc3c6e7","tid":788594,"uid":123991,"like":11,"dislike":19,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"da8683f0b1941747a33fd27796be6c0a5b945750","tid":788594,"uid":14536,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"今日係 21/8"},{"pid":"c75c31180d104d11815e6a2fa20a85963877dea1","tid":788594,"uid":25391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"冇事嘅"},{"pid":"85d2b1e35b2db1ea74456892de0a94cf05f5e255","tid":788594,"uid":199291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"2747b79ef0c9e4bc94f51904afbafb375b2ac005","tid":788594,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"你女朋友有左你仲會唔會開膠po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c05b2ce4ab091b40260e88c09e13132a9ecc1ab","tid":788594,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":